Package: AffyGEx
Title: Affy_hugene_2.0 Pipelines
Version: 2.0
Authors@R: person("Ahmed", "Sadik", email = "ahmed.asadik@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Ahmed Sadik
Maintainer: Ahmed Sadik <ahmed.asadik@gmail.com>
Description: This package was developed for functions mainly used for analyzing AFFY_Hu_Gene 2.0 ST arrays. The package extends easily for other Affymetrix exon and gene arrays. Other applications are possible, especially for downstream analyses.
